The '''Neetakka clan''' was a [[Rodian/Legends|Rodian]] clan on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Rodia/Legends|Rodia]] that emerged around the time of the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]]. The name "Neetakka" meant "Ultimate [[Hunting/Legends|Hunters]]" in [[Rodese/Legends|Rodese]], following the trend of younger clans to take grandiose names.

Despite rising among modern urban environment, the members of the clan dedicated themselves only to their [[species/Legends|species's]] main ancestral activity of [[hunting/Legends|hunting]] and refusing to pursue other careers. As such, they spent all their time honing its hunting skills to live up to its name. A few other clans considered the clan to be bloodthirsty goons, despite grudgingly acknowledging their excellence in hunting.

